		</li>
		<li>
			<a href="/social"
				><Icon name="mdi:account-group-outline" class="h-5 w-5" />
				 Social
				<MenuIndicator isActive={activeBadge === "social"} />
			</a>
			<ul>
				<li>
					<a href="https://github.com/itsjordanmuller"
						><Icon name="mdi:github" class="h-5 w-5" />
